<section class="primary-content">
  <p>Wing it Wednesday™ rides depart from the corner of Turner Lane and High Street, <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/ArXDRXnkWEr">Whiston</a> at 7:30pm prompt.</p>
  <p>Wednesday club rides are much shorter than a Sunday ride, both our road and MTB rides last around 90 minutes. Road rides are run at our standard club pace of about 13-14mph and MTB rides are run at aout 9-10mph.</p>
  <p>When the weather is better in the Summer months we may nip to the pub afterwards for cheeky pop or two.</p>
  <p>Please take time to read our <strong><a href="<%= asset_path('SitwellCyclingClubSitwellCCGenericRiskAssessment–RoadRides2016.pdf') %>">Risk Assessment</a> on Road Riding</strong>.</p>
  <h2 id="upcoming-rides">Upcoming ride</h2>
  <div id="rides">
    <% if (facebook.length > 0) { %>
      <article class="post post--event">
        <h3 class="post__title">Wing it Wednesday™</h3>
        <time class="post__date"><strong><%= facebook[0].date.day %> <%= facebook[0].date.date %> <%= facebook[0].date.month %> at <%= facebook[0].time %></strong></time>
        <p class="post__summary">
          Leaving from the corner of Turner Lane & High Street at 7:30pm.<br><br>
          Our standard Wednesday night ride consists of a local short route lasting no longer than 1 hour 30 minutes.<br><br>
          We go at a pace to suit all. Newcomers welcome. <br><br>
          Ride discription:<br>
          A few lumps and bumps, but nothing too strenuous.<br><br>
          If the weather's nice we'll pop to the Sitwell Arms for a pint afterwards.<br><br>
          Depending on whether you opt for the road or an MTB ride the pace will be about:<br>
          Road - 13-14mph<br>
          MTB - 9-10mph<br>
        </p>
      </article>
    <% } else { %>
      <p>Sorry, we have no planned rides at present. Please check out our <a href="/club-rides/saturday-saunter">Saturday Saunter</a> or <a href="/club-rides/sunday-cafe-run">Sunday Café Run</a> rides.</p>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</section>

